data.description: Move in ready!  You'll love the open floor plan in this 3/2/2 Oakdale home. Entertain guests with the custom built-in bar in the dining room. Enjoy quiet evenings by the wood burning fireplace. Escape to the isolated master with en suite bath. Neutral colors throughout.  New carpet and front screen door with sliding glass to let the fresh air in on nice days. New windows in dining room. Storage building, raised playhouse and dog run in the backyard. Conveniently located close to Rick Husband Amarillo International Airport and Comanche Trail Golf Course.
